reviewText: Love this soap opera. Watching it on TV. I was hoping that this DVD would have subtitles. I'm hispanic, though my spanish is not all that great. So it would have been nice to understand it better.
wonderful thank you so very much

Fue un bonito novela. La persona tiene una buena descripcin de las novelas, pero la persona tiene los nombres totalmente equivocado. Victoria le nombre de su hija es Maria Desamparada (no Cristina)de su hijastro es Maximiliano (no Luis Alfredo) y el nombre del padre es Padre Juan Pablo (no Padre Angel De Jesus. Si era para comprar esta novela me pongo la descripcin errnea de la novela.

It was a nice novella. The person have a nice description of the novellas, but the person got the names totally wrong.  Victoria's daughthers name is Maria Desamparada(not Cristina) and her stepson's name is Maximiliano (not Luis Alfredo) and the priest's name is Padre Juan Pablo (not Padre Angel De Jesus. If was to buy this novela I would get the wrong description of the novela.
The soap opera was in great condition nothing much to complain about it. It was some parts cut from the soap opera but i guess its not that bad.
